			<h3>Биография :</h3>
			<ol>
				<li><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8C,_%D0%91%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%B7#%D0%9E%D0%BF%D1%8B%D1%82%D1%8B_%D1%81_%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B9_%D0%A2%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%87%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%BB%D0%B8">Опыт с трубкой Торричелли</a></li>
